25:34.032 --> 25:38.870 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Tonight, we look at one aspect
of the two
Americas what we're calling news
divisions.

25:38.904 --> 25:43.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
White House correspondent John
Yang went to
Arizona recently to examine how
people get

25:43.308 --> 25:47.445 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
their news and the impact that
