29:00.638 --> 29:03.174 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DELIA SALVATIERRA: Yes, I think
so.

29:03.208 --> 29:04.976 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I think I do that naturally.

29:05.009 --> 29:11.216 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I wish that I could tolerate
watching FOX
News a little bit more, but I
can't, because

29:11.249 --> 29:15.153 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it's usually the same time that
