Anderson Cooper or Don Lemon,
and they're

29:15.186 --> 29:16.154 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
asking questions.

29:16.187 --> 29:17.622 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
