Laura Ingraham and from FOX, you
feel pretty

30:06.037 --> 30:07.605 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
much -- you feel confident in?

30:07.639 --> 30:10.942 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MARCUS HUEY: I have a track
record and history
with them.

30:10.975 --> 30:16.648 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And I feel they both have been
