some kind of a startling
headline, I might

30:21.319 --> 30:25.123 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
hold back and look for other
opinions.

30:25.156 --> 30:36.668 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CNN and MSNBC, I feel it may not
