39:48.586 --> 39:52.690 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Kevin Dillon runs
Connecticut's
Airport Authority.

39:52.723 --> 39:58.529 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
