40:40.771 --> 40:45.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the bottom line is that the
profits from
overbooked flights, infuriating
fees and cheaper

40:46.010 --> 40:49.647 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
