52:56.573 --> 53:00.443 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
The feeling of actually
belonging, it's self-created.

53:00.477 --> 53:06.383 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Arriving at the process of
creating something
from the inside out, it's really
just a validation

53:06.416 --> 53:08.251 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
of existing.

53:08.285 --> 53:12.322 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It matters that we add to the
conversation,
so it's not just one voice
that's being told

53:12.355 --> 53:13.490 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
in picture books.

53:13.523 --> 53:15.192 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It matters.

